Class CoalesceTest

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test

    public class CoalesceTest
extends BaseJDBCTestCase
    Coalesce/Value tests for various datatypes coalesce/value function takes arguments and returns the first argument that is not null. The arguments are evaluated in the order in which they are specified, and the result of the function is the first argument that is not null. The result can be null only if all the arguments can be null. The selected argument is converted, if necessary, to the attributes of the result.
